data.description: Price Reduction!!!! Stone Park at Pike Road is a great place to live and GROW!  This home offers a fabulous floor plan featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, open kitchen, great room, dining room, and foyer. Great room is not only open to the kitchen, foyer, and dining room but it also boasts vaulted ceilings to the second level giving you the feel of breathtaking, spacious living. The laundry room is located right off the 2-car garage and a half bath is conveniently located near the kitchen.  The main bedroom has enough room to comfortably fit a sofa, dresser, desk and chair for an office, as well as a large bed with accommodating furnishings.  The ensuite features two separate vanities with storage, a garden tub, separate shower, water closet, and a large walk-in closet. UPSTAIRS Enjoy the split living quarters featuring 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath.  One of the 3 bedroom may be used as a bonus room for an office, study, entertainment room, or gym. There is access to floored attic space and a linen closet. The landing overlooks the large great room and kitchen.  OUTSIDE The screened patio has a tv and gas fireplace designed for entertaining and relaxing in all seasons while taking in the beautiful scenery of the backyard. The backyard is one of the larger yards in the area! French drains were added to backyard in 2021.  All tv's attached to the walls remain, as well as the refrigerator, Ring doorbell, and 3 surveillance cameras. This is a must see! Other amenities include Community pool and clubhouse with workout room. If this home "checks off" your boxes for your next new home, schedule an appointment with your favorite REALTOR for a personal tour today!
